OWB MorphOS/AROS is a WebKit-based browser originally based on Sand-Labs/Pleyo's implementation. Since then, it has been extensively developed to become a full-blown desktop browser with modern functionality.

OWB Repository: https://github.com/deadwood-pl/OdysseyWebBrowser
OWB MorphOS: http://fabportnawak.free.fr/owb/
Webkit project: http://webkit.org
